_sText:
Are you ready to jump, bhop, strafe and everything you need to parkour?

It is your time to create your own style of a playing on this map.

Create escape paths, fast routes and everything you need in this Mirror's Edge styled CSS map.

There's two sides: Cops and Runners. Runners (Terrorists) have to kill all CTs and CTs must do same.

All have knifes, but can you find 1 Glock that is hidden in this map?

File includes: Mirror's Edge Theme FY_City_Freerun.bsp and Readme.
